criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. ≥18 years old, male or female;

          2. Patients who received allogeneic peripheral blood hematopoietic stem cell
             transplantation ;

          3. Patients must be able to understand and be willing to participate in this study and
             sign informed consent.-

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Non-allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation patients;

          2. The expected survival rate is less than 3 months after transplantation;
